com.hazelcast.util.collection

Class BiInt2ObjectMap<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.util.collection.BiInt2ObjectMap<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - type of the object stored in the map.

    public class BiInt2ObjectMap<V>
extends Object
    Map that takes two part int key and associates with an object.

    The underlying implementation use as Long2ObjectHashMap and combines both int keys into a long key.
